out0 = spark.sql(f"""
    SELECT
   '{Config.sourceSystem}' AS SRC_SYS_CD
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.STARTHISTORYDETAILID) as BTCH_STRT_HIST_DTL_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.CONTAINERID) as CNTNR_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.PRIORITYCODEID) as CNTNR_PRIR_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.MFGORDERID) as MFG_ORDR_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.ccfAncillaryJob) as ANCIL_JOB_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.BATCHCOMMENTS) as BTCH_COMT_TXT
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.BATCHID) as BTCH_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.cscBatchNumber) as BTCH_NUM
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.cscBatchRecipeId) as BTCH_RECIPE_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.BATCHSTATUSID) as BTCH_STS_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.cscBatchTypeId) as BTCH_TYPE_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.BILLOFPROCESSID) as BILL_OF_PRCS_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as BULK_PACK_TYPE_CD
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.CARRIERID) as CARR_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CTN_VERIF_DETAIN_STS_CD
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as CASE_LBL_RCNL_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as CASE_VERIF_DTTM
, INT(StartHistoryDetail.CHANGECOUNT) as CHG_CNT
, INT(StartHistoryDetail.CHILDCOUNT) as CHILD_CNT
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as COLL_DHR_LINE_12_CD
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.CONTAINERCOMMENTS) as CNTNR_COMT_TXT
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CNV_PARNT_LOT_NM
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.QTY2 AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as CUR_2_QTY
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.QTY AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as CUR_QTY
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.CUSTOMERID) as CUST_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as DVC_ID
, case when starthistorydetail.duedate = '00000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(starthistorydetail.duedate,\"yyyymmdd\") end as DUE_DTTM
, case when starthistorydetail.duedategmt = '00000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(starthistorydetail.duedategmt,\"yyyymmdd\") end as DUE_GMT_DTTM
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.cscEquipmentId) as EQMNT_ID
, INT(StartHistoryDetail.cscEquipmentRunNumber) as EQMNT_RUN_NBR
, case when starthistorydetail.expirationdate = '00000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(starthistorydetail.expirationdate,\"yyyymmdd\") end as EXPN_DTTM
, case when starthistorydetail.expirationdategmt = '00000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(starthistorydetail.expirationdategmt,\"yyyymmdd\") end as EXPN_GMT_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as EXPN_UDI_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as EXPT_IMPT_KEY_VAL
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as FOIL_STS_CD
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.HISTORYID) as HIST_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.HISTORYMAINLINEID) as HIST_MNLINE_ID
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IN_QC_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_AUTH_FOR_DESTRUCTION_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_AUTO_STRT_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_CARR_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_DSTRY_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_FAIL_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_INIT_RECON_CMPLT_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_INTRO_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_INV_LOC_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_LAST_SPLT_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_LOT_ABRT_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_LOT_CNV_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_LOT_REV_CMPLT_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_MSTR_LOT_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_PLC_VERS_REQ_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_RCNLD_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_RTRN_FOR_DESTRUCTION_IND
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as JLN_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as LBLS_RCNLD_IND
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.ccfLastParentId) as LAST_PARNT_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.LOCATIONID) as LOC_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.ccfMaintenanceReqId) as MAINT_REQ_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.ccfMaintenanceStatusId) as MAINT_STS_ID
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as MFG_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as MFG_GMT_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as MFG_UDI_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as MSTR_LOT_NM
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.MASTERRECIPEID) as MSTR_RECIPE_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.CDOTYPEID) as OBJ_TYPE_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.OPERATIONID) as OPR_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.OWNERID) as OWN_ID
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.PLANNEDQTY AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as PLAN_QTY
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.PLANNEDQTYUOMID) as PLAN_QTY_UOM_ID
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.PLANNEDQTY2 AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as PLAN_2_QTY
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.PLANNEDQTYUOM2ID) as PLAN_2_QTY_UOM_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.PLANNEDPRODUCTID) as PLAN_PROD_ID
, case when starthistorydetail.plannedstartdate = '00000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(starthistorydetail.plannedstartdate,\"yyyymmdd\") end as PLAN_STRT_DTTM
, case when starthistorydetail.plannedstartdategmt = '00000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(starthistorydetail.plannedstartdategmt,\"yyyymmdd\") end as PLAN_STRT_GMT_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as PLCDHR_MSMCH_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as PLCDHR_NO_DATA_IND
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.PRODUCTID) as PROD_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as PRDTN_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.RECIPELISTID) as RECIPE_LIST_ID
, CAST(NULL AS INT) as RECON_CNT
, case when starthistorydetail.requestdate = '00000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(starthistorydetail.requestdate,\"yyyymmdd\") end as RQST_DTTM
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.RESOURCEID) as RSRS_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as RWRK_CASE_VRFY_CD
, CAST(NULL AS INT) as RUN_SEQ_NBR
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.SALESORDERID) as SLS_ORDR_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as SMPLG_LOT_ID
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.SAMPLINGREQUIRED as BOOLEAN ) as SMPLG_REQ_IND
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.cscSamplingResult) as SMPLG_RSULT_CD
, INT(StartHistoryDetail.ccfSequence) as SEQ_NBR
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.STARTREASONID) as STRT_RSN_ID
, CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as STRT_QTY
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.cscTotalPendingQty AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_PEND_QTY
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.cscTotalQty AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_QTY
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.ccfTotalThruputQty AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_THRUPUT_QTY
, CAST(StartHistoryDetail.ccfTotalThruputQty2 AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TOT_THRUPUT_2_QTY
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.TXNID) as TXN_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as UDI_CD
, INT(StartHistoryDetail.UNITCOUNT) as UNIT_CNT
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.UOMID) as UOM_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.UOM2ID) as UOM_2_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.VENDORITEMID) as VEND_ITM_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as WIP_STS_CD
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as WRK_STN_ID
, TRIM(StartHistoryDetail.WORKFLOWSTEPID) as WRKF_STEP_ID
, CAST(NULL AS INT) as YR_NBR
FROM  {Config.sourceDatabase}.StartHistoryDetail as StartHistoryDetail
WHERE StartHistoryDetail._deleted_ = 'F'
  
 
""")
